data.description: Rare configuration of a 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home located on a large lot in the highly sought after 78745 Western Trails Estates neighborhood. Less than 15 minutes from downtown, it provides convenient access to major highways, the airport, Central Market, and hotspots within walking distance, like El Alma and Radio. Inside, you'll find an updated interior with quartz counters and hard surface floors that has also preserved the original 1960’s vintage style, such as built-in bookcases, formal sitting and dining rooms, a galley kitchen, and custom cabinetry. Home comes with Google Fiber, the full suite of appliances (W/D) and dishwasher, stove, fridge (all purchased new in 2023). All major upgrades have already been done for you - premium HVAC installed in 2023, hot water heater replaced in 2021, foundation stabilization completed with lifetime warranty, and cast iron plumbing has been replaced with PVC. Multiple bedrooms allows extra living space for family, home office(s), and guests. The large two-car garage is great for storage or a home gym. Outside, the large back yard offers a covered patio for your morning coffee or gatherings with friends and family. It also boasts a rare creek-front lot, perfect for enjoying evenings around the fire pit. Don't miss this opportunity to make 2405 Remuda Trail your new home.
